Meaning of Map of Life

Flower of Life

To describe its structure, it is a geometrical shape consisting of overlapping circles, which are spaced out in six-fold symmetry to give it the look of a flower. As is seen from the image above, the flower reflects perfection and harmony. Taken to be a shape known to all religions of the world, it has been more recently named as 'sacred geometry' by the Pagans. So, this particular design is known to depict the fundamental forms of space and time. As mysterious as it may sound, the flower of life is a concept that explains or tries to establish the patterns of the creation of this world; the world as it has emerged from the 'Great Void'. A crucial implication of this shape is its display of how all beings are interconnected. So, it is said to be the ultimate registry with all information of living beings, called an 'Akashic Record'. As per theosophy, an Akashic record maintains a record of all occurring thoughts, words, and actions, as they are impressed upon the 'Akasha' (Ether). In Hinduism, this 'Akash tattva' is considered the primal natural element from which the other four (fire, water, earth, and air) evolved. You may notice the hexagonal pattern, where the center of every circle lies on the circumference of six other surrounding circles of the same diameter. Looking at it as numbers, there are in all 19 complete circles encircled by one big circle on the outside. The following sections discuss some more symbolic arrangements derived from the original form.

Seed of Life

This is a formation where the inner seven circles are placed in six-fold symmetry. As the name suggests, the seed of life forms the basic element of the whole design. In Christianity and Judaism, this stands for the 7 days of creation, when the Judeo-Christian God created life. The vesica piscis is the intersection of two circles of same radius, with the center of each circle lying on the circumference of the other. This shape was the accomplishment of the first day, to which one circle was added per day, leaving the seventh day to be the day of rest, or sabbath. A circle is assumed to be the start of the formation of the seed of life. There are some who believe that it was an octahedron (a polyhedron with eight faces) which was the first step. This shape was to spin on its axis, and then form a sphere. This sphere is identified as the abode of the creator's consciousness.

Tree of Life

The tree of life is commonly associated with the Kabbalah, or the esoteric discipline and school of thought in Judaism. In Kabbalah tradition, it is used to understand the nature of God. The tree of life symbol refers to the idea of common descent. This, being a universal theme in all theologies, is found to be adopted by some Christians, Jews, Hermeticists, and pagans. It is also believed that the 'tree of life' of the Kabbalah is similar to the 'tree of life' as given in Genesis 2:9.

Earth's great spirit will be displayed on your walls!

Please Note: Map of Life ' World Maps are available with 2 different dimensions.

>>HOW TO APPLY<<
Simply wipe clean your surface, peel off the top portion of the wallpaper backing, and apply to your surface starting at the top and working your way down. Remove switch plates and outlet covers before application. Quick to install and easy to get a professional look!

>>ABOUT OUR WALLPAPER<<
Sweet Pea Wall Design removable wallpaper is gorgeous, vivid wallpaper that is easy to put up, is extremely durable, and comes off with absolutely no residue left on the wall. Our self adhesive wallpaper peels off with just a pull, like the perfect sticker. Feel confident trying something bold! Perfect for novice DIY-ers because it's easy to reposition if you need to.

No extra glue, no soaking, no dry time, and no special equipment needed to apply.

Do not apply the wallpaper to freshly painted surfaces, or surfaces painted in the last four weeks. For best results, apply to smooth, light-colored surfaces.

Washable with mild soap and water.

>>STANDARD SIZING<<
We offer sizes based on typical uses in the home:
27" wide x 32" high - common height from floor to low counter
27" wide x 64" high - common height from counter to ceiling
27" wide x 96" high - standard ceiling height

>>CUSTOM SIZES<<
We can create custom sizes to reduce the amount of trimming you have to do. Please message us the specific design and sizes you'd like, and we'll create a special listing for you.

>>SHIPPING<<
Shipping for the Tester Kit is free within the United States, and takes 3-5 business days to arrive once shipped. International shipping is $3 and takes 6-10 business days to arrive.

>>DISCLAIMER<<
The colors displayed on your screen may be different from the actual wallpaper color, as the exact color you see depends on your screen settings. The scale of the pattern in the display images may be different from the actual scale when printed.

>>QUESTIONS<<
If you have questions, just send us a message via Etsy, or email us at sweetpeawalldesign [!at] gmail.com and we'll be happy to help you! We do our best to reply very promptly.

Name: Mini DIY Farmers' Cheese Kit- 3-5 batches
Description:
It may be teenie* but this Mini Farmers’ Cheese Kit is packed with fun and cheesy possibilities. This cheese is fittingly rustic and very adaptable. It can vary from ricotta to feta in flavor and texture. You can use it creamy, firm, sweet or savory - the instructions will guide you!

WAIT! Scroll way down for details/FAQs, double check shipping address and add gift note at check out please.

KIT INCLUDES:
- Instructions with Tips and Variations
- Unlimited Email Support as Needed
- Fine Mesh, 100% Cotton Cheesecloth also known as Butter Muslin
- Gluten-free, Non-GMO Citric Acid
- Pure, Non-Iodized Flake Salt

WHAT YOU NEED:
Simply add milk and in under an hour you will be eating and sharing your very own fresh cheese! No aging required! Pasteurized store-bought or raw farm-fresh milk both work. Make sure your store bought milk is not ultra-pasteurized or UHT, ultra-heat pasteurized.

DIETARY GUIDELINES:
The Mini Farmers’ Cheese Kit is gluten-free, Non-GMO and vegetarian friendly.

QUANTITY:
The Mini Farmers Cheese Kit makes 3 batches of cheese. A batch is about 1 lb so you will have plenty of supplies to try your hand at not only making the cheese but experimenting with different flavors, shapes and recipes. Use bowls, cupcake tins etc. as molds at home.

GOOD TO KNOW:
One of the many unique characteristics of this cheese is that it doesn't melt, so you can actually pan-fry cubes for a browned, crispy, chewy, crazy good treat. Use it instead of croutons on a crisp green salad, fry it like an egg for an amazing sandwich, replace meat or tofu in any dish or just dip cubes as appetizers in a delicious sauce (BBQ, plum, pesto, salsa...) You can make a veggie dip, ricotta cheesecake, mix with jam and top pancakes, use it savory to fill pasta shells, dollop onto chili, layer in lasagna, or crumble onto salads like feta.

The possibilities are endless!

FOOD SAFETY AND HANDLING:
The kits and supplies are hand-poured, hand-folded and assembled in a SQF Level 2, FDA and HACCP certified facility that strictly follow the Department of Agriculture cleaning guidelines. The food items are all gluten-free but packaged in a room that may come in contact with wheat, soy, corn, nuts and other food allergens.

SHELF LIFE for the Mini Farmers’ Cheese Kit is 5 years.

For more information visit www.urbancheesecraft.com

Name: Celtic Tree of life - Handmade Copper Tile. Material - 100% Copper, Stainless Steel or Brass
Description:
Celtic Tree of life - Handmade Copper Tile. Material - 100% Copper, Stainless Steel or Brass

Available in four sizes :

7,87 x 7,87 Inches (20 cm x 20 cm)

9.84 x 9.84 inches (25 cm x 25 cm)

11,81 x 11,81 Inches (30 cm x 30 cm)

15,74 x 15,74 Inches (40 cm x 40 cm)
It is possible to put the tile in the frame and hang it on the wall.

Material - 100% Copper, Covered with patina and wax.



This handmade copper backsplash tile shows a metaphor and a research tool introduced by Darwin in order to visualize his view on relationships between living and extinct creatures, as well as similarities between different species. Since the tree of life raises a timeless question of life and evanescence, it is an extremely popular theme in contemporary art.


Installation and maintenance

My durable backsplash tiles are 0,2" thick (0,6 mm) and very easy to install - just like regular tiles, using about 0,18" (3 mm) grout. Moreover, the maintenance is not a problem. Use 1/2 cup of liquid dishwashing detergent and 2 cups of warm water or mild soap solution. Use a soft cloth or rag, not an abrasive sponge, nor a pad. When cleaning the tile's surface, wipe it gently then rinse the cloth or rag with warm water. Wipe the tile's surface until you make sure that any soap or dishwashing detergent residue is removed. Then dry the surface with a soft cloth or a rag.

Name: 5th Anniversary Gift, Photo on Wood, Picture on Wood, Wood Anniversary Gift, 5 Year Anniversary, Wood Wedding Gift, Custom Wood Burning
Description:
If you're searching for the perfect 5th anniversary gift or gift for any other occasion, look no further than our rustic wood photos. A wood anniversary gift is a great, traditional option for your 5th year of marriage. Not only are our custom pictures on wood ideal for anniversaries, but also make perfect gifts for weddings, housewarmings and so much more!

ABOUT OUR WOOD PHOTOS:
Have your own custom photo printed directly onto round basswood, with no margins or gaps. The photograph becomes an integral part of the wood, ensuring that it will stand the test of time. The natural wood shows through the photo for a beautiful, rustic, and "worn" look. It is said that wood elements within your home can bring balance to your space and life.

Purchasing as a GIFT? Add-on our gift wrapping option and have your custom wood photo wrapped in a natural burlap gift bag - https://www.etsy.com/listing/522661329/burlap-gift-bags-gift-wrapping-add-on

DETAILS:
• Because this is wood from a real tree, pieces may have knots which we try to place in the best spots possible for the photo provided.
• Each piece of wood will vary in wood grain, making each one completely unique.
• Measuring anywhere from 9" to 12" in width or height, depending on the direction of your photo.
• Photos will be cropped around the corners/edges, as this is the only way to fit a rectangular photo onto an oval piece of wood. All important aspects of the photo should not be located along the very edges of the picture.
• Horizontal photos will be placed horizontally on the wood & vertical photos will be placed vertically unless otherwise requested.
• White ink is not printed on the wood. This allows the natural grain of the wood to show through the photo. Colors of the photo on the wood may vary, as these are printed onto natural wood and not bright white paper.
• A clear protective coating is applied over your wood photo to help protect against stains, water and scratching.
• All wood photos come with complimentary hardware for hanging. Stands are not included, but can be purchased separately.
• The bark of the wood is not removed from the wood in order to preserve the natural look of our wood photos.
• All orders are securely packaged with extra bubble wrap for added protection during shipping.
• Made and Handcrafted in Virginia, U.S.A

CHOOSING YOUR PHOTO:
• The better quality the photo, the better the results will be on the wood.
• A 300 dpi photo taken in good lighting will give you the best possible print results.
• Lower quality photos can be used, but please know that the quality will be the same on the wood.
• Extremely dark, blurry, grainy or low-quality photos do not typically transfer well.
• We ask that you DO NOT add any text to your photo, due to cropping reasons.

ENGRAVINGS:
• Looking for a way to make the back of the wood as beautiful as the front? Consider adding on one of our back of wood engraving options.
• Select from a variety of premade and personalized designs and have them ENGRAVED onto the back of your wood photo.
• Scroll through listing photos to see available engraving options.
• Our custom text engraving option allows you to have any custom text engraved onto the back of the wood in the font that is shown. There is no character limit, but the longer the text is, the smaller it will be to fit onto the wood.
• Our custom handwritten text engraving option allows you to add handwritten text to the back of the wood. For handwritten text, please send us a message through Etsy with an attachment that includes a digital or scanned copy of the handwritten text that you'd like engraved. Handwritten text MUST BE ON A PLAIN PAPER BACKGROUND. Text written on lined paper or paper with background designs will not work. The clearer the text is, the better the engraving will be.
• Please keep in mind that because this is real wood, there may be some natural knots/marks on the piece. These may be more noticeable on the back of the wood than on the front, as there is no photo to cover them.

HOW TO PLACE AN ORDER:
1. Purchase this wood photo listing along with any upgrades that you'd like from the drop-down menus.
2. Send us a high-quality digital photo to use through Etsy messages by simply clicking the "ask a question" link or "contact" link on our shop. Attach your photo to the message by clicking on "attach image" or the camera button and selecting your desired photo.

FULL PRODUCT LINE:
View our complete line of products and size options at www.woodphotos.com

Name: The Sasuraibito Tarot - 78 Card Deck and booklet
Description:
The Sixth Printing! ❤️

My complete 78-card original art tarot deck.

The Japanese word: "sasuraibito" most closely translates to "wanderer." It's an old-fashioned literary term that is falling out of use, meant to describe a person ever-seeking, searching for a place of healing and refuge. This deck is designed to aid the curious wanderer, and accompany you on your adventures to come.
This 78 card deck is inspired loosely by the Raider-Waite deck, contemporary living in the Western world, and Japanese and Buddhist concepts and ideals.

The cards measure 2.75''×4.75'' (70mm×120mm) on 330gsm (super smooth) glossy card stock, and are encased in a beautiful, sturdy lidded box featuring the card back design.

Also included is a 63-page guidebook, with brief notes on the meanings and symbolism of my cards. The deck is loosely inspired by the Rider-Waite tarot deck. While some cards follow common iconography fairly closely (Strength, The World), others diverge strongly from tradition (Death, Judgment). Common themes in the deck are the key points in the cycle of life, embracing endings and keeping the fool's open mind.

I painted the original designs between 2015-2017, in sumi ink, watercolor and Windsor & Newton Inks. The original major arcana deck lives in the personal collection of a patron in New York.

Thank you so much for looking!

Back to the shop: https://www.etsy.com/shop/stasiab

Name: Kitchen Equivalent / Measurement Conversion Chart Mason Jar Decal Set - Great Gift Idea! Full Set - Includes Cup & Spoon labels!
Description:
This listing is for my Mason jar themed measurement conversion chart and utensil label decal set, perfect for organizing your kitchen!

I created this set because I had measuring cups and spoons cluttering up precious drawer space and I could never find what I was looking for. This got them out of the way, made them easy to find, and let's be honest... they look great! I shared my photo on Facebook and it went viral, it's been shared hundreds of thousands of times!! It took some coaxing but now I'm offering these decals by popular demand :)

This listing is for the full set of decals (as pictured), with the mason jars conversion charts as well as spoon/cup labels. If you just want to purchase the conversion charts or the label utensils separately you can do so here ---> https://www.etsy.com/LatigoLace/listing/503308073/mason-jar-kitchen-conversion-chart-or?utm_source=Copy&utm_medium=ListingManager&utm_campaign=Share&utm_term=so.lmsm&share_time=1552068981234

If your measuring set has additional utensil sizes not listed here, you can request those sizes in the "notes to seller" box at check out. I'll throw them in for no charge :)

{GENERAL SIZING}
I recommend you measure the width of the area you want the decal and select the next size down. For example: My cabinet is 19" wide but it's a shaker style cabinet so I only measured the inset panel, which is roughly 14.5" wide so I used the next size down, the 14" size.

{CUSTOMIZATION}
If you would like a custom size just purchase the next size up and leave your custom size request in the comment section at check out. For example. If you want an 11.5" wide decal, please purchase the 12" size and I'll scale it down to your specifications. If you would like a utensil label in a size that's not listed I can add that as well, no charge, just put the request

{COLOR}
The color refers to the text. I used a black decal on the cabinet pictured because the wood tone is fairly light. If you have dark cabinetry I would recommend a white for contrast.

{GIFT WRAPPING}
This is an optional add-on. If you purchase gift wrapping with your decal you will receive your order in a white envelope, embellished with a jute twine bow and cute mason jar gift tag. It will ship in another envelope so the gift stays clean and presentable. This really takes it to the next level for gifting!

If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to ask. I will do my best to get back to you right away. Thank you for your business :)

Name: Marsala Maroon, blush pink, ivory, champagne mix of flower petals, Wine rose petals, Burgundy table decor, flower girl petals, wedding decor
Description:
Marsala Maroon, blush pink, ivory, champagne mix of flower petals, Wine rose petals, Burgundy table decor, flower girl petals, wedding, baby decor

*****Please note the completion and shipping timeframe is due to a high volume of orders. And please notate your "NEED-BY" date in your order so I can get the petals to you before then.*****

I hand cut satin fabric and singe each flower petal. The petals will have an appearance of burnt singed edges, so please understand this is how they will look. I singe some a little longer to give the wilting look as that is what real life petals look like.

Various sizes range from 1" (2.5400 cm) up to 3" (7.6200 cm) in diameter.

Conversion from inches to cm:
1" = 2.5400 cm
2" = 5.0800 cm
3" = 7.6200 cm

Prices/amount of petals:
Sample of petals =$2.50
25 petals =$5
50 petals=$10
75 " = $15
100 "=$19
150 " =$28.50
200 " =$38
350 " =$63
500 " =$90
1000 "= $170
2000 “=$320

Link to 1000 petals
https://etsy.me/2Pth299

Link to 2000 petals
https://etsy.me/2Zx9976

FAQ's
Q) How many petals will I need for decorating both sides of the wedding aisle?
A) It depends on how full you want it. You could use 500-1000 petals sparingly. 1000-2000 petals medium fill. 3000-5000 for pretty full.
Q) How many petals are needed to decorate reception tables?
A) I usually suggest 25-45 petals per 8-top table.
Q) I have 2 flower girls, how many petals will I need for them?
A) Flower girls ages 2 & under I recommend 25-50 petals since they may not understand what to do. Ages 3 & older 100-150. But it is also up to you how full you want them scattered.
Q) Are these petals bio-degradable?
A) I would say no, but they would over a long period of time. They are made from satin fabric, they are not "Real" petals. So check with your venue to clarify that satin petals are allowed.

Please message me for any other questions. I'll be happy to try and help.

Please message me if you are in need of a different color and I will do my best to match your color.

For Special Orders: Please allow ample time for finding your special order fabric color and time for completion, some could take 30 days to complete your special order.

If you would like a different size of petal I can custom your order that way as well.

Description:
By popular demand the 'no cats! scaredy mice' sticker is now available in a miniature size! This one should fit even the smallest of skirting boards!

These mice are holding a tentative protest against the cats in your home! Although they probably won't be successful in scaring off any felines, they are guaranteed to make visitors smile! Name: Love Letter Blanket: Personalized Gift for Mom, Woven Handwriting Throw for Dad, Mother's Day, Grandparent, Wedding, Graduation, Anniversary
Description:
** Shipping outside the USA? International shipping is currently highly delayed due to the pandemic, and orders may take 30-60+ days to arrive. **

** Get 10% off your next order by signing up for my mailing list at www.frankieprintco.com/signup **

Write your own custom letter to a loved one so they can wrap themselves up in love. Make it extra personal by using your own handwriting, or keep it simple by using a font!

Makes a great gift for Mother's or Father's Day, Christmas, Valentine's Day, a wedding anniversary, graduation, memorial or birthday! Write your letter to your mom, dad or parent, your child, newlyweds, your husband, wife or partner, your teacher, or BFF. Or a "note to self"!

Sizes:
37"x52" - small size for a chair, or kids blanket.
60"x50" - most popular size, great for throwing on a couch. Pictured in 1st photo.
80"x60" - fit a few people, or use as a bedspread. Approximately the size of a queen size bed (just the top, not hanging down the sides).

100% cotton and machine washable (wash in cold, tumble dry on low). Color is a natural un-bleached cotton (off-white/cream), with black writing, and red + blue lines. The reverse side is blue/green (see photos).

➜ OPTION ONE: Choose the standard handwriting font (shown in the photos), and simply enter your text in the personalization section. I will send you a preview via Etsy message (usually within 48 hours). After you have approved it, it will take 4-8 business days to make. If I do not receive a reply from you within 7 days, I will make the blanket as-is. The faster you reply to this preview message, the faster I can make the blanket :)

OR:

➜ OPTION TWO: Use your own handwriting! Simply print the template (http://bit.ly/LoveLetterEtsy), write your letter, and then scan it (or take a clear photo). After I have received your letter, it will take 4-8 business days to make. This option does not have a preview, and your blanket will look exactly like the template you submit.

Important Notes:
✦ Handwritten letters MUST BE WRITTEN ON THE TEMPLATE provided. I cannot currently work with letters not on the template, but have received many requests for this, so it may be available in the future. Follow me on Instagram for updates on this!
✦ The text you submit must be your original writing, or you must have authorization from the original writer. I cannot use COPYRIGHTED WORK such as poems or music lyrics.
✦ RUSH ORDERS or rush shipping are not available, sorry. Please check the expected delivery dates before ordering.
✦ Once the order has started production, I cannot cancel or change it. Please check your order before submitting it, including the shipping address.
✦ Because this is a custom-made and personalized item, I do not accept returns. However, if there are any errors or quality issues, please contact me within 7 days of receipt with a photo and description of the issue and I will happily fix it.

Name: Classic Walnut Coffee Table - Modern Wood Furniture Mid Century Eames Style Hardwood Design
Description:
________________________________________________________________________________________
Port Rhombus is a husband/wife Industrial Designer duo on Etsy since 2010
In 2016 we moved to rural Thailand! (Still USA owned and operated by us)
View & Favorite our full shop here: www.etsy.com/shop/portrhombus
Music Label: https://unfamiliarenvironments.bandcamp.com/
_______________________________________________________________________________________
DIMENSIONS; Height: 36" wide, 18" deep, 16" tall. (90cm x 45cm x 40.5cm)

This beautiful and incredibly detailed engraved hardwood side table top is made from gorgeous, Grade-A solid walnut butcher block. The tapered legs are solid hardwood and turned by hand for a classic mid-century, rustic-modern style. The legs screw into metal plates underneath the table top for convenience of storing/moving. The tabletop is slightly thinner at 7/8" (22mm) instead of a standard 1" (25mm) to add to the streamlined look of this airy modern design. Details on finish and joinery below.

*DHL Express Delivery requires your phone number so please enter into the comments section of your order to prevent delivery delays. This information is provided to the postal service only, we do not use for marketing or share this information with anyone else.
_______________________________________________________________________________________

Not all tables are created equal! There's many opportunities for short cuts that can reduce the lifespan or enjoyment of a product you might purchase. We're transparent about how our tables are built:

CONNECTIONS:
On our tables you'll never find an non-reinforced joint. We always use dowels, tongue and groove or mortise and tenon joints on all wood to wood connections.

FINISH:
3 stage oil finish of outdoor quality materials to resist the white spots and rings that plague other lower quality waterborne finishes . Grain is sealed inside the wood before top coats are applied for long life. Our Hybrid finish gives you the look of a hand rubbed natural finish with the greater abrasion protection of harder synthetic finishes without looking too glossy or plastic. Only easy, occasional finish maintenance is required to renew your furniture for its life.

Thank you so much for viewing our work and if inclined please view our full shop. As industrial Designers and craftspeople we make a wide variety of products always with attention to detail, clean lines and interesting materials. Matt & Mix - port rhombus design
www.etsy.com/shop/portrhombus


SHIPPING:
*Please note - in regards to shipping price - we not only offer lower prices for solid walnut furniture than most other studios to make our products more accessible, we actually subsidize the shipping cost for you already as well. Typically the shipping prices we charge are already discounted by 30% or so, as such we cannot offer any further shipping discounts*

This item ships in a custom manufactured box that is double-thick corrugated to get to you safely. We try to maintain stock but if built to order it takes 1-10 days to make this table. From there it's and average of two weeks on average for delivery time but we can arrange an express delivery for you as well which is generally 4-7 days at a higher shipping cost. These shipping time estimates are averages, occasionally inclement weather and customs inspections might happen at random and add some time to the delivery which is beyond our control. Finally, while its extremely rare (due to the way we fill out the forms) in the event that a customs duty is imposed as per standard practice it is the purchaser's responsibility to pay the fee. International shipping fees from Thailand are basically a flat rate per kilogram so there are no multi-item discounts for larger furniture items although multiple item discounts are available for small items and will be applied automatically when added to the cart.

RETURNS: In the event of a manufacturer defect upon arrival we will update components, replace the work if needed etc. Due to the high costs involved unfortunately we cannot allow returns based on personal preferences. If you have any special concerns please contact us and we'd be happy talk over any details with you.

Name: Pallet Sign, Pallet Art, Anniversary Gift, 5th Anniversary, Custom Photo Pallet, Pallet Wall Art, Rustic Home Decor, Picture Frame, Wood
Description:
FREE FAST SHIPPING! RUSH PROCESSING AVAILABLE! Your photo printed directly onto a beautiful high quality, handcrafted pallet made from thick premium wood. Custom Sizes available!

ABOUT OUR WOOD PHOTO PALLETS:

We strive to create the highest quality wood photos. Our photo pallets are handcrafted from scratch in our workshop and printing facility located in Virginia. Each pallet slat is cut from thick Grade A, hand selected, Baltic White Birch and then sanded by hand to prevent chipping (a defect often passed-on as "rustic"). Pallets are then assembled and your photo is printed onto and sealed into the surface. Our printing process allows the wood's natural grain and mineral deposits to show through the photo making each piece unique. Because we are involved in each step of the creative process, we can assure the highest quality photo pallets at a low price, as well as guarantee our work. A photo pallet from MyWoodPhoto is a truly handmade piece of art.

We offer a variety of stocked Standard Sizes and offer Custom Sizes as well.

STANDARD SIZES (SQUARE AND RECTANGULAR OPTIONS AVAILABLE FOR EACH SIZE):
Mini One Plank 4x6"
Small 6x6" or 6x9"
Medium 8x8" or 8x12"
Large 12x12" or 12x18"
XLarge 18x20" or 18x24"
Grand 24x24" or 24x30"

CUSTOM SIZES:
We can create wood photo pallets in any size. Please contact us for details and pricing.

CUSTOM TEXT can be printed on the back of our pallets (60 to 100 character limit). Text will be printed smaller on vertical photos due to space restrictions. Text is not available for our Small Pallet sizes due to space restrictions.

COLOR ENHANCED OPTION:
When a photo is printed onto wood the image absorbs some of the natural wood color. Our Color Enhancing service involves a process of whitewashing the wood prior to printing. This allows the color of the image not to be absorbed by the wood. The result is a wood photo with colors that are brighter and more striking while retaining the natural wood grain which makes the piece unique. All Grand Sizes (24x24 and 24x30) include Color Enhanced.

We are happy to add a FREE PERSONALIZED NOTE with the order for the recipient. Simply write what you would like to say in the "Add a Note" section at checkout.

HOW TO ORDER:

1) Pick the size and quantity you would like and purchase this listing.

2) Attach your image in an Etsy message to us and we will immediately begin the process of making your wood photo pallet.

3) Once complete, we securely pack and offer FREE SHIPPING for each order!

Please feel free to ask us any questions you may have. We look forward to making your wood photos!

Name: In This House We Believe Wood Sign / Black Lives Matter / Equality Sign // Home Decor / Love is Love / Women's Rights // Contact for Custom
Description:
This custom-turned-permanent listing encapsulates so many of our values! From the top it says:

In this house, we believe:
Black Lives Matter
Women's Rights are Human Rights
No Human is Illegal
Science is Real
Love is Love
Kindness is Everything

This makes the perfect addition for your home or office, or in the office or home of your social justice oriented friends!

**SIZE
This sign measures approximately 10in by 17.5in, but if you would prefer to have it on a larger sign, we can definitely accommodate that!

**WOOD
The signs are made using select pine wood. Due to the fact that we are not machines (we have the blisters to prove it!), some of the panels of the sign may not be perfectly uniform (1/16th of an inch is our margin). Also, your sign may be slightly lighter or darker than the one pictured, depending on the mood of the wood.

**LETTERING
You can choose vinyl or painted letters. Vinyl is best if you are looking for more of a clean cut look (as in the main picture), whereas paint is more "rustic" and imperfect/distressed (see 4th picture).

**CUSTOMIZATION** (contact us first)
If you'd like to customize this in some way (either changing colors or adding/taking away parts of the board) that is not in our dropdown, go ahead and send us a message with your idea! If it's doable (which it likely will be) then we'll give you an estimate. To make this estimate, we take into consideration the cost of materials, the additional shipping and additional work. For example, changing 1-2 phrases might count as "minor," whereas adding a panel may count as "medium." Once we come to a decision, we'll let you know which customization option to choose.

Please note that the larger signs weigh almost 2x the regular size and subsequently cost more to ship, and thus the price you see includes the customization fee as well as the extra cost of shipping.

***Again please contact us FIRST so we can discuss which option makes most sense!***

**WEATHER PROOFING
If you'd like to hang this sign outside, please choose the paint option and let us know in the "notes to seller" that you want outdoor sealant. To be specific, we use the Olympic® MAXIMUM® Waterproofing Sealant Clear, which offers three years of protection. Please note that you will have to reapply sealant periodically and that it will be somewhat shiny (vs. matte).

**SHIPPING
Please know that we are working as hard as we possibly can to get these signs cut, sanded, and stained as fast as possible while also ensuring each one is made with lots of attention, love and care.

Thank you for stopping by!

A set of 100 discount wood slices.

***Why are these discounted?***
Stringybark Supplies has a strict quality control process and wood slices that do not make the grade for our full price products end up here.

Common reasons slices end up in the seconds box:
• Bark missing or coming off
• Cut unevenly
• Cracked/split
• Misshapen/elongate slices
• Side branch nubs

Name: Vanilla from Uganda| Gourmet Bourbon Type Vanilla Vanilla Beans
Description:
Ugandan Vanilla Beans, A Exciting Addition To the Bourbon Vanilla Family

Gourmet Vanilla beans from Uganda also known as Bourbon Vanilla beans or Vanilla Planifolia are some of some of the best vanilla beans in the world. There high vanillin content and beautiful fig, chocolate and buttery fragrance compliment any recipe or homemade vanilla extract. These beans are plump and supple with a rich oily gloss and very pliable. All specifications meet international grade A standards for vanilla beans.

Grade A vanilla beans conform to the following:

14-16cm Premium Grade vanilla beans
Moisture content of 28-35 percent
Notes of fig, chocolate, creamy Gourmet Vanilla Beans


*A note about purchasing vanilla beans by weight: Vanilla beans are an agricultural product that vary in size, shape, length etc from crop to crop and year to year. Please be aware that you may not receive that exact amount of vanilla beans you are expecting due to the above mentioned size and shape variations when purchasing vanilla beans. It should also be noted that vanillas value is base on weight and weight alone from a market perspective. Simply because the count of vanilla beans is less does not mean you are getting any less product since the value in weight vanilla is still greater. If you need to ensure that you receive an exact amount of whole vanilla beans we recommend purchasing a specific quantity amount rather than purchasing a weight variation.

Description:
** CUSTOM INSTRUCTIONS: Please write the name/quote you would like customized in the "Leave a note to RSVPpartydecor" box on the checkout page, or message us directly after ordering. **

This listing is for one (1) custom cake topper made from thick glitter cardstock. Your custom name or quote will be written in the font as indicated in the listing photos.

- Please note that in order to ensure the quickest production & delivery, design previews will only be sent if specifically requested in the order notes. Design previews are only available after the order is placed. There is a 5 word (maximum) limit to a custom cake topper. -

❤ RSVP Party Decor cake toppers look beautiful on top of cakes, and can also be used for many more purposes. Our cake toppers are perfect for decorating desserts, table centrepieces, flower arrangements, fruit bowls & much more! They can also be used as momentum pieces after your event, such as in photo collages, picture frames, or shadow boxes. ❤

ღ IMPORTANT INFORMATION ღ
Please read our Shop Policies and listing descriptions before purchasing. Our FAQ below provides highlights of some of our policies for your review. By placing an order with us, you are agreeing to our shop policies. Always feel free to message us here on Etsy if you have any questions – We are happy to help!

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
🌟 MATERIALS
* Premium, thick glitter cardstock. There is glitter on the front only - the reverse (back side) of the topper is matte white.

* White lolly stick. We carefully glue a white, food-safe lolly stick to each of our toppers. Some cake toppers may require 2 sticks rather than 1 depending on the stability and/or size of the design.

🌟 SIZE
Select the cake topper width upon checkout. All sizes are measured in inches. You may refer to our sizing guide (included in the listing photos) for size recommendations.

The height of the topper varies depending on the width selected. This cake topper is attached to a white, food-safe lolly stick, which is about 3 to 4 inches in height.

🌟 COLOUR
Please select the colour you would like by using the dropdown menu. All colour options for this topper are made with one-sided glitter cardstock (glitter on one side, matte white on the other side).

🌟 QUANTITY
This listing is for one (1) cake topper. Multiple quantities are available. Our cake toppers are made-to-order, so we can make as many as you would like. Please select the quantity you would like by using the drop-down menu.

🌟 PRODUCTION & SHIPPING TIMES
Please visit our Shop Announcements for current production/processing times. Shipping times vary depending on the destination and the service selected at checkout. Please see our FAQ below or our Shop Policies for further information regarding shipping.

🌟 CUSTOM MADE
Select the colour and size for this product using the dropdown menus. The custom text can be written in the order notes.

The text will be written exactly as spelled in the order note. Notes left in all capital letters will be converted to Capitalized Case (the first letter of each word capitalized). Due to the cursive nature of the font, the topper cannot be made in all capital letters to ensure optimal readability. Notes left in all lowercase letters will be made in all lowercase.

Since the colour, size and text are made to your specifications, this item is considered a custom product and therefore all sales are final.

🌟 DESIGN PREVIEWS
We strive for a very quick production turnaround time (1 to 3 business days). To ensure that your order will be shipped as soon as possible, design previews for personalized products are not provided unless specifically requested in the order notes.

🌟 WHOLESALE
Wholesale pricing is available when purchasing multiple of the same design. Please see our FAQ or message us before ordering to inquire about a wholesale order.

🌟 CARE INSTRUCTIONS
While we do use the thickest glitter cardstock on the market, please be aware that cardstock is a paper product. Some designs may be fragile. Please carefully remove your cake topper from the packaging. Cake toppers are best stored face-down (glitter side down) on a hard and dry surface. It is best to handle cake toppers by the stem (do not hold the cardstock/design area). We work our hardest to ensure that all cake topper designs are as stable as possible. When handled with care, cake toppers can be used more than once or saved as a momentum (i.e. in shadow boxes, frames, photo collages, etc).
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Lapis Lazuli stone (Truth - Wisdom - Serenity) is said to help enhance your awareness, insight and truth. One of the most sought after stones in use since man's history began. Its deep, celestial blue remains the symbol of royalty and honor, gods and power, spirit and vision. It is a universal symbol of wisdom and truth. In ancient times Lapis Lazuli was most highly regarded because of its beautiful color and the valuable ultramarine dye derived from it. Its name comes from the Latin lapis, "stone," and the Persian lazhuward, "blue." It is rock formed by multiple minerals, mostly Lazurite, Sodalite, Calcite and Pyrite, and is a rich medium to royal blue with gold flecks (pyrites). Lower-grade Lapis is lighter blue with more white than gold flecks, and is sometimes called denim Lapis.

Lapis Lazuli stones make wonderful tools to deepen your meditation during your yoga practice. Lapis Lazuli is a powerful crystal for activating the higher mind and enhancing intellectual ability. It stimulates the desire for knowledge, truth and understanding, and aids the process of learning. It is excellent for enhancing memory. A stone of truth, Lapis encourages honesty of the spirit, and in the spoken and written word. Wear it for all forms of deep communication. It is also a stone of friendship and brings harmony in relationships. A Lapis grid brings calm and loving communication.

Name: Gifts for Chefs, Knife Roll, Chefs Roll, Knife Bag, Chef Gift, Leather Knife Roll, Chefs Bag, Chef Knife Bag
Description:
I'm not a cook, but I know how to make great bags. So it wasn't a surprise when a very famous Master Chef asked me if I can make a knife roll for him. We worked together for about a month, cutting and sewing and measuring again and this is what we created. A rough beauty, a comfortable bag for his precious knives and an object of envy for other chefs.

It has 10 slots of different sizes perfect for your knives and other cooking utensils. There's plenty of space to hold the knives, the tongs and tweezers, a sharpening stone and your gloves. We also made a pocket for a mandolin.

The bag is made of saddle leather and it has a nice sheet of waxed canvas to protect the knives. Even so, I suggest to use your own blade covers, for the leather to be happy.

You can carry it by the handler, but you can also put in on your shoulder. The shoulder strap is made of two layers of leather and is adjustable.

I think it's a perfect knife roll for all the cooks, masters or not.

WASHING
It is recommended to wash linen in the machine (choose the delicate cycle, (40 C/104 F) without overcrowding with similar fabric and colors. To maintain the color, we advise not to use bleach and avoid exposure to continual sunlight. We suggest using a mild liquid detergent such as a wool wash.

DRYING

IRONING

Name: Eiffel Tower Ornament Wood cut Eiffel Tower Decoration J'aime Paris Ornament
Description:
Wood ornament of the Eiffel Tower, intricately cut from 1/8" wood. Approximate size is 5.75 by 4.75 inches (14.5 x 12 cm) with a Red ribbon at the top for hanging.

This ornament depicts the very picturesque Eiffel Tower in Paris, France. The words "J'aime Paris" (I love Paris) are added to remind us of the beautiful area and how we would like to return! It was built in 1889 as the entrance arch to the 1889 World's Fair.

An Ornament such as this is often bought around the holidays or as a souvenir. It can be hung from a desk lamp, on a wall, in a window or on a Christmas tree.

Name: Bamboo Pendant Light - Handmade Wooden Pendant Lamp Hanging Repurposed Fishing Trap Basket, Hanging Natural Woven E27 Boho Rustic Lamp World
Description:
A traditionally handwoven Thai bamboo fishing trap, re-purposed into a beautifully minimalistic pendant light.

Various sizes available - For reference, the basket in the majority of pics is size C.

Oblong is the natural shape but they can be made spherical and other shapes easily.

The basket is compressible/expandable like a concertina and can achieve many shapes and position - the oblong shape is the natural position/shape - the round shapes as shown in the listing pictures for example are achieved simply by compressing from each end, and tying the supplied string inside to pull taut as shown to then hold in desired position.

e.g The third picture shows standard oblong baskets, one of which has been made into a round ball shape.


[ About ]


A classic example of Asian craftmanship, these fishing traps are handwoven from natural bamboo using techniques that are centuries old. We've added a simple yet precise hanging lamp holder that can be adjusted with an adjustable metal support bracket so that you can position your bulb anywhere inside the basket, along with a choice of ceiling rose to match your style/theme.

The basket can be opened/closed like a concertina to get a variety of shapes and fixed in position with string, from the long droplet style to a round circle.

'Basket Only' option includes the metal cord bracket and cord grips.

Different color ceiling roses, lamp holders and cable lengths/styles are available upon request, feel free to send us a message.



[ Cable length ]

The cable can be made to any length. If you would like a specific length not in the listing options, simply purchase the closest meter from the listing options and add in the order notes the specific length you require. For example, if you would like a cable length 265cm, purchase the 3m option and add the 265cm request in the order notes. We would then make a cable set that is 265cm long.

If you require longer than options listed, you can purchase additional length by the meter here, and same thing applies : https://www.etsy.com/listing/631615382/additional-cable-length-lighting-cable

Length is visible cable.



[ Details ]


○ Traditionally handwoven / handcrafted Thai fishing trap basket from natural bamboo.

○ Choice of natural wood or white metal ceiling rose (with screws & attachments) - OR - 2pin or 3pin plug ( UK & US )

○ E27 / E26 lamp-holder with silicone or natural wood cover

○ Adjustable metal support bracket for holding basket

○ Natural rope or clean white PVC cable (other lengths and colors available upon request)

○ Voltage 110V-250V

○ 60 Watts Max.



[ Approx. measurements ]


Sizes may differ slightly as each is handmade. Approx ranges are below.


-- When in natural OBLONG shape --

Size A - Overall height : 85-90 cm / 33-36" | Diameter : 38-43cm / 15-17"

Size B - Overall height : 70-75cm / 27-30" | Diameter : 30-35cm / 12-14"

Size C - Overall height : 60-65cm / 23-26" | Diameter : 27-32cm / 10-13"

Size D - Overall height : 50-55cm / 19-22" | Diameter : 23-28cm / 9-11"

Size E - Overall height : 45-50cm / 18-20" | Diameter : 20-25cm / 8-10"

Size F - Overall height : 38-45cm / 15-18" | Diameter : 18-23cm / 7-9"


-- When in ROUND / SPHERE position --

Size A - Diameter : 58-63cm / 23-25"

Size B - Diameter : 43-48cm / 17-19"

Size C - Diameter : 40-45cm / 16-18"

Size D - Diameter : 25-30cm / 10-12"

Size E - Diameter : 20-25 cm / 8-10"

Size F - Diameter : 18-23 cm / 7-9"



-- Ceiling rose diameter (both natural and white styles) - 10cm



[ Options ]

Basket Only - includes just the bamboo basket, without cable/lamp set (*includes the metal bracket and cord grips for using with your own cable/lamp set if necessary)

Natural Ceiling - includes the bamboo basket and fully assembled cord/lamp set with wooden lamp holder and rope style cable, with a a wooden ceiling rose for connecting to your existing electrical wiring in the ceiling/home.

Natural Plug - includes the bamboo basket and fully assembled cord/lamp set with wooden lamp holder and rope style cable, with a plug on the end to plug into your home electrical socket like a lamp etc. The light is turned on and off at the plug / no cable switch.

White/Black Plug - includes the bamboo basket and fully assembled cord & lamp set with white/black silicone lamp holder and white/black PVC cable, with a plug on the end to plug into your home electrical socket like a lamp etc. The light is turned on and off at the plug / no cable switch.

White/Black Ceiling - includes the bamboo basket and fully assembled cord & lamp set with white/black silicone lamp holder and white/black PVC cable, with a a white/black metal ceiling rose for connecting to your existing electrical wiring in the ceiling/home.



[ Notes ]

○ The light bulb is not included. We recommend softer energy saving LED or weaker vintage style bulbs as seen in the pictures to protect the bamboo from heat damage.

○ As each piece is individually handmade they will differ slightly in size, shape and shade, and may have small marks and wear.

○ Oblong baskets will be folded/flattened for easier delivery but this has no effect on their shape or strength due to the unique design - simply filling out and 'pumping' a few times like an accordian will restore the original oblong shape.



[ Shipping ]


Our lamps are packed with loving care and sent from Northern Thailand via tracked airmail which should reach you in around 12-21 days standard airmail (US, UK, EU, AUS, ASIA), or 5-7 days via Express.

Please be aware that VAT is NOT included - for some countries (typically EU countries) VAT and customs duties may apply, these are the responsibility of the buyer. If the item is returned to us due to non-payment of the customs duties/fees we would be unable to refund the original shipping cost.

Shipping discounts are available for multiple orders.

(For more detailed shipping estimates and information please see our main shipping policy.)



[ Questions and queries ]


If you have any questions please send a message and we will get back to you asap.

Description:
Create your own vinyl decal! This decal can be customized and personalized with any text. Lots of color and font choices to choose from, choices are shown in the listing photos. If you would like a logo or image please contact me with a photo BEFORE ordering to make sure it is something we can do.
**Please do not request trademarked logos or slogans, we will not reproduce these.

**IMPORTANT SIZING INFORMATION**
The size you choose will be the longest length of the design by the maximum height of the design. For example, if you choose the 10" x up to 5" size, your decal will be 10 inches long and up to 5 inches tall.
The actual height will depend on the specific text you want and your font choice. Please contact me with the details for your order if you would like to know the exact height.
*If no font is specified, you will receive the font pictured.

**If all information needed to create your decal is not provided with your purchase, your order could be delayed**

**SHIPPING INFO**
*Please check the shipping tab for the current processing time.
*Standard shipping is USPS First Class Mail which is estimated to arrive in 2-5 business days.
*Priority Mail is estimated to arrive in 1-3 business days depending on your location but is not guaranteed.
*Express Mail is guaranteed 1-2 day delivery depending on your location.
Please contact me for more information about shipping upgrades.
****Choosing a shipping upgrade does not change the processing time, only the shipping time****
*If you need your item(s) by a certain date and that date falls before the listed processing time plus shipping time please contact me BEFORE ordering to make sure I can I can get it to you in time.
*A rush fee may be needed depending on the size of the order and how soon it is needed.

*Please note due to due to different computer screen settings color may differ slightly*

*All of my decals are shipped with transfer tape and application instructions*

All items are shipped usps first class mail with tracking and insurance against loss or damage.

Acceptable Application Surfaces
•Glass
•Metals (Must be painted with a smooth, glossy enamel.)
•Vehicles (Must be painted with a smooth, glossy enamel.)
•Vinyl (Such as Banners, Canopies, flags, etc.)
•Plastic
•Fiberglass (Must be painted with a smooth, glossy enamel.)
•Wood (Must be painted with a smooth, glossy enamel.)
•Other Painted Surfaces (Paint must be smooth and glossy, vinyl will not stick to oxidized, faded, or peeling paint)

Not Recommended Surfaces
•Cement
•Raw Lumber
•Oxidized or faded paint
•Peeling paint
•Rubber
•Raw Metals
•Oily Surfaces

These lists are not comprehensive and there are other acceptable and unacceptable substrates than those listed above. Again, when in doubt, apply the rule that states vinyl will generally adhere well to hard, smooth, glossy and clean surfaces.

*DIFFERENCES IN MATTE AND GLOSS VINYL*
Gloss vinyl has a glossy finish and matte vinyl has a flat finish. As a general rule, matte is for indoor use and gloss is for outdoor use. You can use matte vinyl outdoors, but it will not stick as long as gloss vinyl, and you can use gloss vinyl indoors but it has a sticker adhesive backing and may be harder to remove from walls or other painted surfaces.
For anything that will be wet or handled regularly I recommend using gloss vinyl.

Name: LARGE Custom Wood Photo, 5th Anniversary Gift, Anniversary Gift, Wedding Picture on Wood, Wood Anniversary Gift, 5 Year Anniversary, Custom
Description:
A custom wood photo is a great alternative to your average picture frame. Why settle for a plain rectangular frame, when you can easily add a little rustic touch into your home decor with your favorite photos printed on wood.

ABOUT OUR WOOD PHOTOS:
Have your own custom photo printed directly onto round basswood, with no margins or gaps. The photograph becomes an integral part of the wood, ensuring that it will stand the test of time. The natural wood shows through the photo for a beautiful, rustic, and "worn" look. It is said that wood elements within your home can bring balance to your space and life.

Purchasing as a GIFT? Add-on our gift wrapping option and have your custom wood photo wrapped in a natural burlap gift bag - https://www.etsy.com/listing/522661329/burlap-gift-bags-gift-wrapping-add-on

DETAILS:
• Because this is wood from a real tree, pieces may have knots which we try to place in the best spots possible for the photo provided.
• Each piece of wood will vary in wood grain, making each one completely unique.
• Measuring anywhere from 12" to 15" in width or height, depending on the direction of your photo.
• Photos will be cropped around the corners/edges, as this is the only way to fit a rectangular photo onto an oval piece of wood. All important aspects of the photo should not be located along the very edges of the picture.
• Horizontal photos will be placed horizontally on the wood & vertical photos will be placed vertically unless otherwise requested.
• White ink is not printed on the wood. This allows the natural grain of the wood to show through the photo. Colors of the photo on the wood may vary, as these are printed onto natural wood and not bright white paper.
• A clear protective coating is applied over your wood photo to help protect against stains, water and scratching.
• All wood photos come with complimentary hardware for hanging. Stands are not included, but can be purchased separately.
• The bark of the wood is not removed from the wood in order to preserve the natural look of our wood photos.
• All orders are securely packaged with extra bubble wrap for added protection during shipping.
• Made and Handcrafted in Virginia, U.S.A

CHOOSING YOUR PHOTO:
• The better quality the photo, the better the results will be on the wood.
• A 300 dpi photo taken in good lighting will give you the best possible print results.
• Lower quality photos can be used, but please know that the quality will be the same on the wood.
• Extremely dark, blurry, grainy or low-quality photos do not typically transfer well.
• We ask that you DO NOT add any text to your photo, due to cropping reasons.

ENGRAVINGS:
• Looking for a way to make the back of the wood as beautiful as the front? Consider adding on one of our back of wood engraving options.
• Select from a variety of premade and personalized designs and have them ENGRAVED onto the back of your wood photo.
• Scroll through listing photos to see available engraving options.
• Our custom text engraving option allows you to have any custom text engraved onto the back of the wood in the font that is shown. There is no character limit, but the longer the text is, the smaller it will be to fit onto the wood.
• Our custom handwritten text engraving option allows you to add handwritten text to the back of the wood. For handwritten text, please send us a message through Etsy with an attachment that includes a digital or scanned copy of the handwritten text that you'd like engraved. Handwritten text MUST BE ON A PLAIN PAPER BACKGROUND. Text written on lined paper or paper with background designs will not work. The clearer the text is, the better the engraving will be.
• Please keep in mind that because this is real wood, there may be some natural knots/marks on the piece. These may be more noticeable on the back of the wood than on the front, as there is no photo to cover them.

HOW TO PLACE AN ORDER:
1. Purchase this wood photo listing along with any upgrades that you'd like from the drop-down menus.
2. Send us a high-quality digital photo to use through Etsy messages by simply clicking the "ask a question" link or "contact" link on our shop. Attach your photo to the message by clicking on "attach image" or the camera button and selecting your desired photo.

FULL PRODUCT LINE:
View our complete line of products and size options at www.woodphotos.com

Description:
This perpetual calendar is artisan crafted from solid hardwood maple to last year after year. It is not only beautiful but a very useful tool in both teaching and organizing your days. Use your calendar to bring attention to the purpose of the day and upcoming events and teach children about weather conditions and cycles of the moon. This calendar brings so much learning and fun while adding beauty and joy to your home.

Each calendar is made to order and depending on our current workload can take from three to four weeks to ship. We thank you for your patience.

Every calendar comes with:

* A 12x13-inch Wall Base
* 6 Reversible Month Cards
* 4 Season Coins
* 8 Weather Coins

Choose from the dropdown menu how you'd like the days of the week finished on your calendar:

"All Natural Days" has the weekdays printed with no background color.
"Waldorf Colored Days" follows the specific colors Waldorf homeschooling families assign for each day, shown in our first photo--Sunday/White, Monday/Purple, Tuesday/Red, Wednesday/Yellow, Thursday/Orange, Friday/Green, and Saturday/Blue.
"Rainbow Colored Days" follows the colors of the rainbow--red, orange, yellow, green, blue, indigo, and violet from Sunday through Saturday.

We can even create a calendar in languages other than English. Simply leave a note during the checkout process if you're wanting something different from English. Shown in the photos above are a couple samples we've made for Chinese and German, but any language can be done.

Name: Cotton anniversary gift - add a new leaf each year of marriage. Applique tree in 8" wooden hoop frame
Description:
This is the perfect wedding anniversary gift! A gift that keeps on giving and that you can add to over the years to symbolise the longevity and growth of your marriage.

When made with two cotton leaves to begin with, this is the ultimate 'cotton' gift for your two year anniversary.

I first made this as a gift for my husband on our wedding anniversary. Now each year on our anniversary I stitch on a new leaf for us. We eagerly anticipated that first addition, and already talk of how our little tree will look when full with colourful leaves.

This listing is for one framed tree applique, made using free motion machine embroidery. I will stitch on the first two leaves for you {if you need more (or less), see my other listings or send me a message with this order}. I will also include a little ziplock bag with about 60 pre-cut leaves in a variety of colours and prints, for you to add on each of your future anniversaries. The leaves have "Bondaweb" already ironed on the back, so are self-adhesive when you iron them. You can iron them on and leave it at that, or you can go on to hand stitch with black around your new leaf. Each little leaf is only about 1.5cm long, so it's not too much work!

The fabric background is linen in a natural creamy linen colour. The tree is dark brown cotton. The first leaves stitched on will be a variety of colours and prints - not necessarily as shown in these images. They are 100% new cotton.

The frame is an 8" (~20cm) diameter wooden embroidery hoop. Because you may need to take the fabric out of the frame for ironing / stitching the new leaves on each year, the fabric will not be adhered to the frame, but I will make the back as neat as possible and ready for display.

** Due to popular demand!
If you'd like to personalise your tree with your names and/or wedding date, please see this listing here where for a small extra fee you can "Add-On" your personal details:

https://www.etsy.com/au/listing/191089830/personalised-wedding-anniversary-add-on?ref=listing_published_alert

Other trees with different fabric types (ie. all green leaves; Liberty of London prints) are also available in my shop:

https://www.etsy.com/shop/tailorbirds

Please check Etsy policies regarding paying customs tax. Recently some European buyers have had to pay a charge to release their order from the post office. Buyers are responsible for this and it is not included in my shipping costs.

Thank you

Description:
Hi there and thank you for viewing my item!

Handmade by NancysJars a retro light lamp made from a VHS. These cool night lights can be made to order for a special, one off, personal gift.

They can be made based on any film, band or actor (Jurassic Park, Star Trek, One Direction, Football clubs) and where possible I will always use an original VHS for that ultimate retro feel. You can also pick what colour lights (this one has blue) or leave it to NancysJars to get creative!

Great to use as night lights in children's bedrooms as there are no cables for plugs and as they are LED they are bright enough to light a room! X2 or X3 AA batteries not included.

A brand new option available is the LED Multi-functional USB powered lamp. You can connect the USB to your computer, laptop, TV or directly into a plug. Light colour can be changed options include blue, red, green, white, yellow and different shades of selected colours. You also have the function of flashing fast, flashing slow, pulsate or multicolored flash. Cable length approx 1m. You can now also upgrade to the Remote control Multi-functional USB light option, its close range infra-red allows you to turn on/off and choose between 16 colour and pattern options :)



If you love this VHS upcycle as much as we do click order now! If love the label style but not the movie drop me a message to discuss a customised option!
Multiple shipping saving available at checkout on all items worldwide :)

Description:
Marsala Maroon, blush pink, ivory, champagne mix of flower petals, Wine rose petals, Burgundy table decor, flower girl petals, wedding, baby decor

*****Please note the completion and shipping timeframe is due to a high volume of orders. And please notate your "NEED-BY" date in your order so I can get the petals to you before then.*****

I hand cut satin fabric and singe each flower petal. The petals will have an appearance of burnt singed edges, so please understand this is how they will look. I singe some a little longer to give the wilting look as that is what real life petals look like.

Various sizes range from 1" (2.5400 cm) up to 3" (7.6200 cm) in diameter.

Conversion from inches to cm:
1" = 2.5400 cm
2" = 5.0800 cm
3" = 7.6200 cm

Prices/amount of petals:
Sample of petals =$2.50
25 petals =$5
50 petals=$10
75 " = $15
100 "=$19
150 " =$28.50
200 " =$38

500 " =$90
1000 "= $170
2000 “=$320

Link to 1000 petals
https://etsy.me/2Pth299

Link to 2000 petals
https://etsy.me/2Zx9976

FAQ's
Q) How many petals will I need for decorating both sides of the wedding aisle?
A) It depends on how full you want it. You could use 500-1000 petals sparingly. 1000-2000 petals medium fill. 3000-5000 for pretty full.
Q) How many petals are needed to decorate reception tables?
A) I usually suggest 25-45 petals per 8-top table.
Q) I have 2 flower girls, how many petals will I need for them?
A) Flower girls ages 2 & under I recommend 25-50 petals since they may not understand what to do. Ages 3 & older 100-150. But it is also up to you how full you want them scattered.
Q) Are these petals bio-degradable?
A) I would say no, but they would over a long period of time. They are made from satin fabric, they are not "Real" petals. So check with your venue to clarify that satin petals are allowed.

Please message me for any other questions. I'll be happy to try and help.

Please message me if you are in need of a different color and I will do my best to match your color.

For Special Orders: Please allow ample time for finding your special order fabric color and time for completion, some could take 30 days to complete your special order.

If you would like a different size of petal I can custom your order that way as well.

Name: Modern Mailbox Large, Walnut Mailbox, Wall Mounted mailbox
Description:
The measurements of the mailbox are 14.5"W x11.5"H x 6"D. Interior dimensions are 13 3/8”Wx 10 5/8”Hx 4 1/4”deep.

This is a made to order item. PLEASE EXPECT 8 WEEKS for the item to ship. Sorry for the long wait time, July seems to be a busy month for me.

The mailbox attaches to an exterior wall by two keyhole brackets located on the back of the mailbox. These brackets are hung from two round head screws that are screwed into your wall. Screws are included.

The wood is sealed with a Coat of marine grade epoxy resin and 2 coats of clear exterior grade spar urethane finish. No stain is applied to the wood. I recommended mounting the mailbox to a wall that has shelter of some kind such as eves, covered porch or an overhang. The bottom of the wood box is cement board. I use this for its water resistance and weight.

A lock can be added to the mailbox. Here is the listing for adding a lock: etsy.com/listing/290962273/add-a-lock
If you would like a lock, this listing should be added to your cart for check out. The lock listing explains how the lock works.

The mailbox can be laser etched with names, numbers or graphics. Etching is $20 extra. Typically the laser burns slightly making the etching darker depending on the wood type but if not I will apply a dark stain in the etching so it stands out.

The mailbox cover is available in stainless steel or powder coated galvanized steel in black, red, bronze or white.

This item is subject to customs duty fees and import taxes when shipped outside the US.

The image shown is not the actual mailbox that you will receive for this listing.

Name: Passionflower (Organic)
Description:
Herbs: Passionflower (Organic)
Passiflora incarnata

Format: C/S
Size: 1 oz

Also Known as: Passiflora incarnata, Passiflora caerulea, Apricot Vine, Blue and Purple Passionflower, and Maypop.

Farming: Organic
Location: Italy

Passionflower is a climbing vine native to South Texas, Mexico, and Central America. Growing to a length of 30 feet (9 meters) under ideal conditions, the vine bears three-lobed leaves, purple flowers, and yellow-to-orange egg-shaped fruit. The name of the plant comes an analogy between the plant’s ornate flower to the elements of the crucifixion of Jesus, white and purple to symbolize heaven and purity, five stamens for the five wounds he suffered, three style for the three nails used to affix him to the cross. A Spanish doctor named Nicolas Monardes was the first to document the flower used in Peru in 1569, which he then brought back to Europe with him, where its popularity spread quite rapidly as a sedative. It was later classified by Linnaeus in 1745, when he noted over 20 species. Nowadays, there are reputably over 400 different species.

The parts used are generally the dried leaves and stems. Passionflower powder must be stored at temperatures below 77 degrees F (25 degrees C), and should be used within six months of purchase. Can be used as teas, tinctures and encapsulations. Sometimes found in relaxing bath blends and sleep pillow mixes

Herbalists in Mexico, Central America, and Texas have used passionflower as a calmative and sleeping aid for over 200 years. Currently there is a German E monograph for passionflower citing its use as having sedative qualities.

NOTE: Pregnant women should avoid passionflower, since it can stimulate uterine contractions. Safe dosages for children under 6 have not been established. Caution should be used buy those on other sedatives as passionflower may intensify the effects.

In Magick, Passionflower is ruled by Venus and Water. It is an excellent herb to use for all types of sleep blends - but especially sleep pillows. It raises vibrations in a room and tend to bring forth a sense of peace and calmness. Excellent for incense blends and sachets when you need arguments to stop, or just to bring about an overall relaxation to everyone involved. Also works well in incense blends for Meditation.

For educational purposes only This information has not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This information is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease.

Description:

You will find these telepathic messages will help and guide you in your life. They will provide answers to your questions. Spirit is in the Past, Present and Future, and they can see and understand everything and also see the outcome of situations and view them with clarity.

Bio

Born 25th December, (Christmas Day)

When I was a child, I knew there was something different about me. I would have a sense of calmness and the reassurance everything would be fine.

Mainly at night, I would see someone standing in the bedroom and at times I felt the unseen host sat on my bed. Shadows would appear on the walls, as I looked at them. I heard a voice calling my name "David."

I was in the Jungle with the British Army, Late at night we came under fire from the enemy, suddenly a spirited soldier looked at me, and a sense of calmness, and the word 'safe,' entered my mind.

Throughout the Uk, I travelled to demonstrate my Clairvoyance on stage. I conducted a private one and one readings to recipients from all backgrounds, from solicitors, doctors, bricklayers, to the housewife.

I was invited to America in which the Native American's sat outside my cabin, waiting for a psychic reading. The energies were potent bring in some beautiful telepathic messages. People from around the U.S. visited me for a one and one private message. I found myself to be a very busy worker.

The sense of excitement knowing I travelled 800 miles across Egypt by hitchhiking alone, not afraid, and the sense of knowing I was protected. It was all worthwhile.

I enjoy helping to raise funds for good causes, such as cancer research, child abuse, homeless, and many more. I would cycle many miles to raise funds, and each time on the road riding my bike, I knew the invisible energies protected me.

Name: Picture on Wood, Custom Photo on Wood, Rustic Portraits, Distressed Portraits, Reclaimed Wood Photo Transfer, Wood Photo Blocks
Description:
A personalized picture on wood is the perfect way to add a little rustic touch into your home decor. With a custom photo on wood, the possibilities endless. Wedding pictures, family photos and pet portraits are just a few ideas of special memories that can be captured on our wood photos.

ABOUT OUR WOOD PHOTOS:
Have your own custom photo printed directly onto round basswood, with no margins or gaps. The photograph becomes an integral part of the wood, ensuring that it will stand the test of time. The natural wood shows through the photo for a beautiful, rustic, and "worn" look. It is said that wood elements within your home can bring balance to your space and life.

Purchasing as a GIFT? Add-on our gift wrapping option and have your custom wood photo wrapped in a natural burlap gift bag - https://www.etsy.com/listing/522661329/burlap-gift-bags-gift-wrapping-add-on

DETAILS:
• Because this is wood from a real tree, pieces may have knots which we try to place in the best spots possible for the photo provided.
• Each piece of wood will vary in wood grain, making each one completely unique.
• Measuring anywhere from 9" to 12" in width or height, depending on the direction of your photo.
• Photos will be cropped around the corners/edges, as this is the only way to fit a rectangular photo onto an oval piece of wood. All important aspects of the photo should not be located along the very edges of the picture.
• Horizontal photos will be placed horizontally on the wood & vertical photos will be placed vertically unless otherwise requested.
• White ink is not printed on the wood. This allows the natural grain of the wood to show through the photo. Colors of the photo on the wood may vary, as these are printed onto natural wood and not bright white paper.
• A clear protective coating is applied over your wood photo to help protect against stains, water and scratching.
• All wood photos come with complimentary hardware for hanging. Stands are not included, but can be purchased separately.
• The bark of the wood is not removed from the wood in order to preserve the natural look of our wood photos.
• All orders are securely packaged with extra bubble wrap for added protection during shipping.
• Made and Handcrafted in Virginia, U.S.A

CHOOSING YOUR PHOTO:
• The better quality the photo, the better the results will be on the wood.
• A 300 dpi photo taken in good lighting will give you the best possible print results.
• Lower quality photos can be used, but please know that the quality will be the same on the wood.
• Extremely dark, blurry, grainy or low-quality photos do not typically transfer well.
• We ask that you DO NOT add any text to your photo, due to cropping reasons.

ENGRAVINGS:
• Looking for a way to make the back of the wood as beautiful as the front? Consider adding on one of our back of wood engraving options.
• Select from a variety of premade and personalized designs and have them ENGRAVED onto the back of your wood photo.
• Scroll through listing photos to see available engraving options.
• Our custom text engraving option allows you to have any custom text engraved onto the back of the wood in the font that is shown. There is no character limit, but the longer the text is, the smaller it will be to fit onto the wood.
• Our custom handwritten text engraving option allows you to add handwritten text to the back of the wood. For handwritten text, please send us a message through Etsy with an attachment that includes a digital or scanned copy of the handwritten text that you'd like engraved. Handwritten text MUST BE ON A PLAIN PAPER BACKGROUND. Text written on lined paper or paper with background designs will not work. The clearer the text is, the better the engraving will be.
• Please keep in mind that because this is real wood, there may be some natural knots/marks on the piece. These may be more noticeable on the back of the wood than on the front, as there is no photo to cover them.

HOW TO PLACE AN ORDER:
1. Purchase this wood photo listing along with any upgrades that you'd like from the drop-down menus.
2. Send us a high-quality digital photo to use through Etsy messages by simply clicking the "ask a question" link or "contact" link on our shop. Attach your photo to the message by clicking on "attach image" or the camera button and selecting your desired photo.

FULL PRODUCT LINE:
View our complete line of products and size options at www.woodphotos.com

Name: Maria S.C. single test tubes chandelier / lamp / // vase / floral decoration
Description:
Maria S.C. chandelier is made from laboratory test tubes, set in two plywood bands. This surprising material and geometric shape makes this lamp both classic and innovative. The double glass cylinder recalls Art Deco forms in a unique contemporary way. The use of ready-made objects gives an appearance with a Duchamp idea. The lamp is inspired by the Polish scientist, Maria Sklodowska-Curie, who was awarded the Nobel Prize in Chemistry. The tubes are detachable and the lamp provides the opportunity for visual experiment by creating a variety of configurations and flower arrangements.

The tubes are detachable and the lamp provides the opportunity for visual experiment by creating a variety of configurations and arrangements.

Diameter: 47cmx47cm (18.5 x 18,5 inches) ,
High: 110 cm (43.3 inches) from celing to the bottom edge.

(If you need the different lenght let us know, we can change it for free)

The package contains:
- one ring with the hanging strings,
- ceramic bulb socket,
- ceramic ceiling rose
- 60 test tubes

Bulb is not included (E27 type, max to 100 Watt)

Tubes are very durable. They should not been broken in transport but you will receive some additional test tubes, just in case.

The lamp is very easy to install. You need it just to hang and put the tubes into the ring.

To arrange the rainbow, we have used food colouring powder (3 basic colors: red, blue, yellow) and mixed it in different proportions. Food powders are easy to remove, they do not color of glass permanently.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Designer: Pani Jurek

Pani Jurek was founded by Magda Jurek, artist and designer. She graduated in painting at the Academy of Fine Arts in Warsaw and brings a conceptual approach to her work with the aim of creating products which are not obvious and not standard. She designs products which can be changed and rearranged together with spaces and which also awaken your own creativity. For example, a lighting fixture turns into a vase, a tablecloth into a playhouse. She credits her design approach in part to growing up in Polish prefabricated apartment blocks during the nineteen eighties. Within limited spaces, products needed to be compact and also multi-functional. She is also an advocate sustainability. With items which can be used in multiple ways, you can limit your purchasing needs.

Pani Jurek is also co-founder of the association “Based in Warsaw” which was set up to achieve social design as well as design for public areas.


https://www.facebook.com/PaniJurek

We ship worldwide, Ask us for the price of international shipping!

Name: Ovoo Balancing Stones- Surprise Stones
Description:
Get a surprise when you order this set, you never know what new and beautiful stones you are going to get!

Mark your own trail! Are you stuck in an office, house or anywhere but outside where you truly want to be? Are you stressed or anxious and needing an outlet? Ovoo stones are a simple but effective way to practice mindfulness, dexterity and add some natural beauty to your space!

Inspired by cairns marking hiking paths throughout the world (without negative environmental consequences) -- Ovoo stones allow you to create rock sculptures in the comfort of your own office or home. You can change them up each day creating a new design. Or you can challenge yourself and balance the stones precariously or order additional stones for an even taller and more striking aesthetic!

Ovoo's are rock cairns near sacred mountains in Mongolia. Ovoo stones can help you create your own sacred space. However, we are givers at Ovoo stones, and we want you to be too. So, a fair donation is made to protect environmental health with every purchase. Each set of 7 stones comes with an agate base with felted wood pulp backing for a soft, level and steady base. The stones come in a muslin pouch suitable for gifts.

Description:
Assorted Tillandsia Air Plants Lot from Aura Creations®

Tillandsias (air plants) have the power to both filter and cleanse the air. Improve the quality of your air with living air plants while beautifying your space at the same time
These adorable creations not only make a lovey addition to any space, and make for the Perfect Gift!

Includes:
- 11 Tillandsia Indoor houseplants
- 1 Organic Plant Fertilizer Food
- Care Instructions
- Support! Any questions please message us :)

**Size: Please note many sellers offer baby Air plants from 1"-2" in size
We wait until our plants Mature. Each is a minimum size of 2" upwards to 5" Inches.

What are Air plants?
Air plants are an incredible genus of plants with the ability to live without soil! Their
specially adapted leaves absorb water and nutrients from the air, allowing them to live anywhere in nature, including suspended from treetops and bare rock. Found in South America and the southern United States, air plants have an amazing variety of shapes, colors, and sizes!

What's the best way to display them?
Because they're so versatile, the possibilities are endless. A single suspended air plant is simple and beautiful, but they can also be arranged in any style and in any area. That's why it's so fun to design with air plants — they can bring nature to any space, indoors or out.

EASY TO CARE FOR-
Air plants are best kept in a bright location to receive indirect sunlight. They only require watering once a week and do not require soil!

*Please expect some slight variation in terms of color, texture, etc., as each is a natural creation unique in character.
